      "body" : "@banarun: Yes - because otherwise it couldn&#39;t be used in an anonymous inner class. Now as of Java 8, local variables can be &quot;effectively final&quot; so this would still work in Java 8 without being explicitly final... but you still couldn&#39;t change it afterwards."
