      "comment_id" : 114885889,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "It&#39;s actually very much like a constructor. I can access protected members of an abstract base class. Everything else can be done in code before instantiating of the anonymous class."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 7421,
